github.setup        facebook rocksdb 3.13.1 rocksdb-

revision            0
categories          databases devel
platforms           darwin
license             BSD

maintainers         stromnov openmaintainer

description         Embedded key-value store for fast storage
long_description    ${description}

homepage            http://rocksdb.org/

checksums           rmd160  7c33dbaaebce86d591b8bc615cac83bad2c9ca94 \
                    sha256  421ee55edec9ae6b3a1d5e69fbaf23dacaf92a21d6fe3d1d5b6da00ac59d2c42

